## Best Practices

### Use OpenAPI Specification

**Benefits**:
- Single source of truth
- Automatic documentation generation
- Interactive documentation (Swagger UI)
- Code generation
- API testing

```yaml
# openapi.yaml Example
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  title: User Management API
  version: 1.0.0
  description: API for managing users
servers:
  - url: https://api.example.com/v1
paths:
  /users:
    get:
      summary: List users
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Successful response
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: object
                properties:
                  users:
                    type: array
                    items:
                      $ref: '#/components/schemas/User'
components:
  schemas:
    User:
      type: object
      properties:
        id:
          type: integer
        name:
          type: string
        email:
          type: string
```

